{"title":"庄稼夫妻","authors":["甄崇德"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":7,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼夫妻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甄崇德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清早，放足水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前晌，插完秧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晌午，开农会；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后晌，锄苗忙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍晚，喂了牛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃罢夜饭，把绳儿扁担放头旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸脚，睡的香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月天长夜儿短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动梦儿不能长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎鸡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打了翅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公鸡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫天亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚过门的新娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍醒了年青的郎："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒啊！醒啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子黄了穗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱去收割忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫，下了炕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子，开门窗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫，门外走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子，担水忙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里，麦子呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄成一片香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猪儿喂饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛儿上山岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子堆成一捆又一捆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排了一行又一行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火着的猛，风箱拉的响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚锅下金米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉米搓成黄干粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压年的黄菜，盐鸡蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子挑好送给郎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子放了担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫蹲树旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子盛上饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫拿干粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人儿庄稼饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼饭儿吃的香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子满脸笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫喜气扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子卷好衣袖包好头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我也来呀！我也来帮忙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夫妻两人动手割，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女哪肯落后方？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手起麦子倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀沙沙响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子倒，倒两行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两人弯腰来捆绑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行十二个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两行捆成十二双，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳升的高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子喷喷香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个满脸笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑脸闪黑光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个喜气扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上有红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个割的快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个劳动强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个年青汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个翻身娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动夫妻勤生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发家致富有指望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身曲儿不用旁人编，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动歌儿自己都会唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地是咱的命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱在土里受苦，土里长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天土地得解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼夫妻有福享，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面有咱领路人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们依靠共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四九年七月于张垣。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}